:FED.
14.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers the posting of security/surety for the payment
of the insured's legal fees as well as demands from the local
authorities for the coverage of any compensation claims raised
against the insured, when such claims have arisen during the journey.
